headline.main: Congo Opposition Party Expels Top Official in Sign of Infighting
headline.print_headline: Congo Opposition Party Expels Top Official in Sign of Infighting

lead_paragraph: Drugmakers Sanofi and Regeneron said on Saturday results from a one-year test of their Dupixent product aimed at adults with eczema or moderate-to-severe atopic dermatitis (AD) had been positive.
